Dialogue: 10,0:47:17.69,0:47:28.65,Song,,0,0,0,,Shout out your feelings loudly \NGo on cry, go on fly
Dialogue: 10,0:47:30.04,0:47:32.70,Song,,0,0,0,,Tell me now baby
Dialogue: 10,0:47:33.21,0:47:36.10,Song,,0,0,0,,I know you must of cried
