Dialogue: 10,0:49:36.42,0:49:39.55,Song,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:49:41.21,0:49:45.40,Song,,0,0,0,,By my side
Dialogue: 10,0:50:29.86,0:50:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Heisei-era perestroika!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:32.21,0:50:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Berlin Wall of anime is coming down!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:38.60,0:50:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In an unprecedented crossover, all of Go Nagai's most popular characters go wild together!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:42.79,0:50:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Reimagined as super-deformed chibi versions,
Dialogue: 10,0:50:45.40,0:50:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,rampaging east, west, south, and north!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:48.67,0:50:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Featuring Devilman, Mazinger Z, \NGetter Robo, Violence Jack,
Dialogue: 10,0:50:52.38,0:50:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and many more in a dream lineup!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:02.38,0:51:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With an all-star staff from the {\i1}Devilman: Sirene Arc{\i0} delivering high-quality slapstick comedy,
Dialogue: 10,0:51:08.80,0:51:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,outrageous gags, and grand, over-the-top scale,\N it's the biggest anime sensation of the century!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:13.20,0:51:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming on video tape and LaserDisc!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:16.11,0:52:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Original Video Animation: \N{\i1}Mobile Suit Gundam 0083: Stardust Memory{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:21.79,0:52:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Answering the expectations of {\i1}Gundam{\i0} fans, \N12 volumes, starting spring 1991.
